      "text": "\nABRAMO, Giovanni, D’ANGELO, Ciriaco Andrea and DI COSTA, Flavia, 2019. When research assessment exercises leave room for opportunistic behavior by the subjects under evaluation. Journal of Informetrics. 2019. Vol. 13, no. 3, p. 830–840. \n"
