    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "1b9149d9ff4faefa",
      "text": "ALI, Lana, 2023. Co-Authorship Network Analysis in Constraint Programming Research. 2023. [https://www.diva-portal.org/smash/record.jsf?pid=diva2:1798590 page] [https://www.diva-portal.org/smash/get/diva2:1798590/FULLTEXT01.pdf pdf] [Accessed 18 December 2023]."
